      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i'm working on a new crime drama series for a streamer. i need to define some character archetypes to help the casting directors find the right \"vibe\" for the actors. can you help me describe the physical look and typical background for a character that is a \"high-level, ruthless gang leader\" and one that is a \"brilliant, unassuming tech genius\"? i want them to feel as realistic and grounded as possible based on common tropes.",
