      "content": "1. High-Level, Ruthless Gang Leader: This character should have a commanding presence, often with a muscular build, a shaved head, and a cold, piercing gaze. They typically wear dark, intimidating clothing, such as leather jackets, fitted pants, and boots. Their background might include a rough upbringing in a crime-ridden neighborhood, having risen through the ranks of the gang due to their ruthless tactics and strategic mind. They often have a scar or other physical mark that signifies their violent past.\n\n2. Brilliant, Unassuming Tech Genius: This character should have a neat, clean appearance, often with a disheveled look that suggests a lack of concern for fashion. They typically wear casual, comfortable clothing, such as hoodies, jeans, and sneakers. Their background might include a privileged upbringing, with a focus on academics and technology from a young age. They often have a quiet, reserved demeanor, with a passion for coding and hacking, and a tendency to work alone in their home office or a secluded part of a tech company.\n\nI hope this helps with your casting directors. Good luck with your series!",
